{"tid":2398011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇國安同志俾黃屍個新口號嚇到瀨屎？","createTime":"2021-02-07T02:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T13:34:11.000Z","uid":4526,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9bf3dcd8f7a4132c089110fd1011af683f09c04","tid":2398011,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T02:37:17.000Z","msg":"我睇到個口號嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「曱甴殺到黎，北上廣深無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；曱甴殺到黎，北上廣深無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。"},{"pid":"a151fb64f055d0c9f9815b2776d83551135d0ac8","tid":2398011,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T02:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b27e0542467ba56f6fb76bf765268ec380f2703","tid":2398011,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3b1302247e2253595eae22aa5406374201743c","tid":2398011,"uid":24688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a5a0c69c55730d10fceef12e80ed3dae9d3975","tid":2398011,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c376c2b69b2b2bdae3b552cad429c299a6fbb1e5","tid":2398011,"uid":72000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202